JO  - Management Science
SP  - 250
EP  - 255
VL  - 29
IS  - 2
PB  - INFORMS
N2  - The geometric properties of the sets of efficient and weakly efficient solutions of multiple linear fractional programming problems are investigated. Weakly efficient solutions are path-connected by finitely many linear line segments when the constrained region is compact.
AB  - The geometric properties of the sets of efficient and weakly efficient solutions of multiple linear fractional programming problems are investigated. Weakly efficient solutions are path-connected by finitely many linear line segments when the constrained region is compact.
